RVI OIC Gateway
---------------
Temporary module to realize the Genivi OIC demo.
Performs translation from OIC to RVI and vice versa.
Implements a minimalistic rule engine via SQLite.
Hosts RVI controls as OIC resources.
Aggregation of OIC responses.
Propagation of responses across RVI and OIC

Pre-requisites
--------------
1. export RVIDIR=<path to RVI folder>
2. export OICDIR=<path to IoTivity folder>
3. Build iotivity library and RVI service.
4. sudo apt-get install libcurl4-openssl-dev sqlite3-dev

